1
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:46,640
Finally.

2
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,760
Why didn't you tell me?

3
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,239
Lu Xixiao,

4
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:00,519
is there

5
00:02:00,519 --> 00:02:01,920
something we should do?

6
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,120
What?

7
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:10,520
Should we

8
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,159
tell everyone

9
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:14,280
we're together?

10
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:23,479
Give me your hand.

11
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,639
Sit still.

12
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,120
So fast?

13
00:02:52,719 --> 00:02:53,759
I've been wanting to post it for a while.

14
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:55,879
I've been waiting for you to give me the chance.

15
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:07,639
When did you take this secretly?

16
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,360
No.

17
00:03:11,879 --> 00:03:12,680
How is it?

18
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:16,199
Can't I keep a record for myself?

19
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:19,199
You didn't even tell me.

20
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,080
Secret.

21
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:29,919
You?

22
00:03:29,919 --> 00:03:31,120
It's coming.

23
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:43,319
So pretty.

24
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:48,919
Are you satisfied?

25
00:03:50,719 --> 00:03:51,439
Who is he?

26
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,479
A junior in school.

27
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:57,759
Senior,

28
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:58,840
do you really have a boyfriend?

29
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,560
I wanted to visit you

30
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,080
in your city after graduation.

31
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,120
Junior?

32
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:03,879
He's not my boyfriend.

33
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:04,639
Junior?

34
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,319
He's indeed my junior.

35
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,840
You have a lot of boyfriends.

36
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:13,000
I'm honest.

37
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:13,879
You can see it.

38
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:15,400
When I was away,

39
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,519
you had a lot of suitors.

40
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,480
You're ungrateful.

41
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:24,240
Don't be a hypocrite.

42
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,879
I can ask Lin Na

43
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:27,800
if you have a conscience.

44
00:04:30,839 --> 00:04:31,639
I'm going to ask Lin Na.

45
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:33,319
I'm going to ask her.

46
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,600
Are you still asking?

47
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:39,959
Who?

48
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,800
Okay, okay, I was wrong.

49
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,000
I'm done with you.

50
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,439
You can't talk about me.

51
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,680
Why is my name tagged as "6"?

52
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,639
Because your last name is Lu,

53
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,839
And six is your number.

54
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:58,480
I was too embarrassed

55
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,560
to put your name,

56
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,879
in case someone saw it.

57
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,040
In case someone saw it?

58
00:05:06,199 --> 00:05:07,319
Am I that embarrassing?

59
00:05:11,279 --> 00:05:11,839
It's because

60
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:13,439
you have many admirers.

61
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,319
I'm afraid of being hated.

62
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,519
Now you

63
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:17,839
are turning the tables.

64
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:18,680
- I find... - It's true.

65
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:27,439
What are you looking for?

66
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,160
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

67
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,720
It's not too late to tell you now.

68
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,560
I like you so much, Lu Xixiao.

69
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,439
Zhou Wan,

70
00:06:51,439 --> 00:06:52,279
I'm hungry.

71
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,079
What do you want to eat?

72
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:54,879
I'll cook for you.

73
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,160
Lu Xixiao,

74
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,160
let's go cook.

75
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,519
Are you trying to strangle me?

76
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:07,399
Put me down, now!

77
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,319
Let's cook.

78
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:09,360
No, no, no!

79
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,040
No!

80
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:15,839
So Jiang Fan

81
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,920
pretended to buy your house

82
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:20,079
from you,

83
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:22,480
and then you remarried?

84
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:24,439
Not exactly.

85
00:07:24,519 --> 00:07:25,720
He just didn't want me

86
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,639
to sell the house,

87
00:07:26,639 --> 00:07:28,000
and he didn't want a divorce.

88
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:30,160
I was really upset.

89
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,319
I thought this time when I went back,

90
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:32,680
I would have a big fight with him.

91
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:33,800
I must get a divorce.

92
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,639
But as soon as I walked in the door,

93
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:38,439
everything was just the furniture and decorations I wanted.

94
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,279
And there was a whole wall of photos.

95
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,680
I cried my heart out

96
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,680
when I didn't see him.

97
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:44,800
You know what?

98
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,480
He's always been the same.

99
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:48,079
Yeah.

100
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:50,079
He's always had me wrapped around his finger.

101
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,439
You're the one who has him wrapped around your finger.

102
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:55,079
I'm not.

103
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:58,519
You've been together for seven years

104
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:02,040
and married for three. It's been a long time.

105
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,399
Every time you had a little fight,

106
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:05,279
he still can't live without you.

107
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:10,600
I feel like I can't live without him either.

108
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,600
So what do you think is the difference

109
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,480
between marriage and dating?

110
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:16,959
There's a difference.

111
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,120
When dating,

112
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,560
two people go out from their own homes

113
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:23,160
to have a date,

114
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:26,040
drink milk tea, and so on.

115
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,519
But after getting married,

116
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:31,639
you go home together

117
00:08:31,639 --> 00:08:33,240
after work.

118
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,720
You always have someone

119
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,559
waiting for you.

120
00:08:36,279 --> 00:08:37,720
No matter what happens outside,

121
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,840
you don't have to face it alone.

122
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,600
Where are we going?

123
00:08:52,759 --> 00:08:54,399
We'll be there soon.

124
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,720
Don't peek.

125
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,120
Okay, I won't.

126
00:08:59,759 --> 00:09:01,320
We're going downstairs.

127
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,159
Be careful.

128
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:05,799
It's okay. Just follow me.

129
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:08,919
One step down.

130
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,159
Two steps down.

131
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:15,200
That's it? You made it so mysterious.

132
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:16,799
We're here.

133
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:23,240
Just a bit further.

134
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:37,879
Open your eyes.

135
00:10:06,759 --> 00:10:08,519
This is the one from the game room.

136
00:10:08,519 --> 00:10:10,480
Yeah, I bought it.

137
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:18,080
It's been years

138
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,039
since we played this.

139
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:21,720
Ten years.

140
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,679
It still works.

141
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:32,039
You bought this back?

142
00:10:33,159 --> 00:10:33,759
What?

143
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:36,279
You want to keep competing with me?

144
00:10:37,159 --> 00:10:38,200
Mr. Gong,

145
00:10:40,279 --> 00:10:41,399
you were right.

146
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,759
I went easy on you back then.

147
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,679
Tonight, I'll make you cry.

148
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,519
You forget how hard you worked

149
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:52,960
at that time, Zhou Wan.

150
00:10:53,759 --> 00:10:55,360
How can you make me cry?

151
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,399
I'm not afraid of you.

152
00:10:56,399 --> 00:10:57,600
I'll teach you how to play.

153
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:58,759
Come on.

154
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,759
You teach me?

155
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,600
You are my defeated opponent.

156
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,559
I let you win at that time.

157
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,159
I'm dead.

158
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:33,360
What's going on?

159
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:35,879
Why didn't you dodge?

160
00:11:37,679 --> 00:11:38,559
I didn't want to.

161
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,000
Lu Xixiao,

162
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,960
you could have dodged

163
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,600
countless times in the past,

164
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,559
but you chose

165
00:12:20,759 --> 00:12:22,039
to lose to me.

166
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,080
This time,

167
00:12:26,759 --> 00:12:28,320
I'm willing to lose to you too.

168
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,480
I like you.

169
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:40,960
I like you, Lu Xixiao.

170
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,120
I've liked you for a long time.

171
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,279
I really like you.

172
00:12:51,399 --> 00:12:52,559
I like you so much.

173
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,120
The old Zhou Wan

174
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,399
was too timid.

175
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:07,000
She never dared to believe

176
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,399
that we would have

177
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,960
a happy ending.

178
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,120
Thank you.

179
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:30,120
Every time I shrink back,

180
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:33,039
you come to me firmly.

181
00:13:35,399 --> 00:13:37,320
Every time I encounter difficulties,

182
00:13:38,399 --> 00:13:39,720
you are the first one

183
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,480
to rush in front of me.

184
00:13:47,679 --> 00:13:48,679
Thank you.

185
00:14:01,919 --> 00:14:03,240
Thank you for

186
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,559
falling in love with me,

187
00:14:08,559 --> 00:14:11,039
who is helpless, weak,

188
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:13,440
poor,

189
00:14:14,879 --> 00:14:16,559
and not kind.

190
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,720
Thank you for making me believe

191
00:14:21,519 --> 00:14:23,159
that the future can bring

192
00:14:23,159 --> 00:14:25,039
good luck and happiness.

193
00:14:30,759 --> 00:14:31,679
Silly girl.

194
00:14:40,279 --> 00:14:41,559
Will you marry me?

195
00:14:46,519 --> 00:14:48,240
Will you marry me, Lu Xixiao?

196
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,360
Yes, I will.

197
00:15:22,679 --> 00:15:23,440
I will.

198
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:30,360
I'm very willing to.

199
00:16:02,399 --> 00:16:04,240
You know you have work today,

200
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:06,320
yet you stayed up so late last night.

201
00:16:12,039 --> 00:16:13,320
You don't have to go with me.

202
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:15,200
You can stay at home

203
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:17,200
and help me confirm

204
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:19,000
the guest list for the art exhibition.

205
00:16:24,639 --> 00:16:26,360
I want to sleep a bit more.

206
00:16:26,679 --> 00:16:28,240
Get up and eat something before you sleep.

207
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:29,960
Or it's bad for your stomach.

208
00:16:31,279 --> 00:16:32,000
No.

209
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:37,320
I want to sleep for another hour.

210
00:16:41,399 --> 00:16:42,559
Alright, go to sleep.

211
00:16:45,559 --> 00:16:46,639
It's a good day.

212
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:53,080
You won't be the only one sleeping.

213
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:53,759
No!

214
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:56,960
You can't tickle me!

215
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:58,240
You're cheating. Will you sleep or not?

216
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,519
I don't want it!

217
00:16:59,519 --> 00:17:00,720
I'm up, I'm up!

218
00:17:01,039 --> 00:17:03,120
I'll have breakfast, I'll have breakfast!

219
00:17:03,399 --> 00:17:04,839
Alright, I'll have breakfast.

220
00:17:04,839 --> 00:17:05,839
I got it, get up.

221
00:17:05,839 --> 00:17:06,759
Get up, sit up.

222
00:17:07,799 --> 00:17:08,480
Sit up.

223
00:17:09,119 --> 00:17:10,960
I'm really speechless.

224
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:18,880
I'm not talking to you anymore.

225
00:17:22,799 --> 00:17:23,759
Don't tickle me.

226
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:34,880
Same old routine.

227
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:37,160
Hang some paintings other than

228
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,200
the First Snow series

229
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,119
at the entrance to the exhibition hall.

230
00:17:39,519 --> 00:17:40,799
And then in this area,

231
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:43,000
hang fourteen paintings

232
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:43,920
of the First Snow series.

233
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:46,160
The four most valuable paintings

234
00:17:46,279 --> 00:17:47,079
will be hung here.

235
00:17:47,559 --> 00:17:48,240
I'll also

236
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:50,880
add some snow-like decorations on the floor,

237
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:53,319
to give the audience

238
00:17:53,319 --> 00:17:54,759
an immersive experience.

239
00:17:56,519 --> 00:17:57,200
This

240
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,799
most prominent spot

241
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:01,400
is reserved for you

242
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:03,519
to hang your four most important paintings.

243
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:07,480
This main background board,

244
00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:09,240
I want to hang the most mischievous painting

245
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:10,720
of the two of you.

246
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:12,640
Hang it in this most conspicuous spot.

247
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:14,799
Okay.

248
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:18,519
Okay.

249
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:20,920
Okay, no buts.

250
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:23,839
Just do as you say.

251
00:18:23,839 --> 00:18:24,599
It's up to you.

252
00:18:28,799 --> 00:18:29,680
It's up to me?

253
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:38,640
What?

254
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:39,599
It hurts.

255
00:18:42,279 --> 00:18:43,119
But when have you

256
00:18:43,119 --> 00:18:44,119
ever listened to me?

257
00:18:47,359 --> 00:18:49,359
Bro, tell me the truth.

258
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,279
Do you have some terminal illness?

259
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:52,480
If you do,

260
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,680
you must tell me right away.

261
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:55,039
I can't live

262
00:18:55,039 --> 00:18:56,279
without you.

263
00:18:56,279 --> 00:18:56,880
without you.

264
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:58,039
Cut the crap.

265
00:18:58,599 --> 00:18:59,759
I'm listening.

266
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:02,880
I know

267
00:19:03,039 --> 00:19:03,759
you're back together

268
00:19:03,759 --> 00:19:04,759
with your little antidote.

269
00:19:07,559 --> 00:19:08,559
Seeing you like this,

270
00:19:09,119 --> 00:19:09,960
I'm truly happy for you.

271
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,440
How's life treating you lately?

272
00:19:20,839 --> 00:19:22,400
A'Xiao is preparing for an art exhibition.

273
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:24,319
I'm here to deliver an invitation to you.

274
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:27,839
I quit my job.

275
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:31,039
I should let go of my past

276
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:32,839
with Lu Zhongyue.

277
00:19:34,319 --> 00:19:35,759
I'm taking my mom out for a trip.

278
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:37,880
When?

279
00:19:38,119 --> 00:19:38,839
Tomorrow.

280
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:40,759
So sudden.

281
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:43,160
I've been thinking for a while.

282
00:19:44,359 --> 00:19:47,240
I used to think about success,

283
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:48,920
but when I look back,

284
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:50,440
[I still don't know]

285
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:51,519
[what I really want.]

286
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:54,599
[I'm leaving.]

287
00:19:58,799 --> 00:19:59,519
[Zhou Wan.]

288
00:20:02,839 --> 00:20:03,839
[Even if we're no longer friends,]

289
00:20:04,119 --> 00:20:05,440
[I can still wish you well.]

290
00:20:08,839 --> 00:20:09,759
[Take care.]

291
00:20:12,519 --> 00:20:13,200
[Jiang Yan.]

292
00:20:16,079 --> 00:20:17,279
[Live for yourself from now on.]

293
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:47,799
It feels like the days of working together

294
00:21:47,799 --> 00:21:48,759
were just yesterday.

