[That was actually our]

593
00:41:25,199 --> 00:41:26,079
[first photo together.]

594
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:27,880
[Although your face]

595
00:41:27,880 --> 00:41:28,639
[wasn't even clear.]

596
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:30,239
[I've given it my all.]

597
00:41:30,639 --> 00:41:31,320
[I have no regrets.]

598
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:32,480
Lu Xixiao, what are you doing?

599
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:50,719
[Every time you appear,]

600
00:41:51,559 --> 00:41:52,880
[you're like a rainbow,]

601
00:41:53,599 --> 00:41:55,199
[You bring color]

602
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:56,199
[to my dull life.]

603
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:40,760
[I've always been afraid]

604
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:42,519
[to tell you how long]

605
00:42:42,800 --> 00:42:43,880
[I've liked you,]

606
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:45,679
[until]

607
00:42:46,559 --> 00:42:48,159
[that summer came.]

